   <talk_paragraph index="n091_trader_bellin-accepting-a" image="QM_HoundNormal_2.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n091_trader_bellin-accepting-b" mid="100" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="95"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Berlin$<BR>But I don't know how I should spend all this money. I filled up all my warehouses...<BR>I can't give this to my hound to play with….</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n091_trader_bellin-accepting-b" image="QN_Npc_Scholar_Starshy.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n091_trader_bellin-accepting-c" mid="101" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Technology?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="96"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Berlin$<BR>So I thought about it for some time, and <FONT color=#a82424> Heraldry Scholar Stas</FONT> asked me whether I want to spend it on investing in new technology that is being developed.<BR>Since it's extra money rotting in the warehouse, I might as well help a hungry scholar.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n091_trader_bellin-accepting-c" image="QM_HoundNormal_2.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n091_trader_bellin-accepting-d" mid="103" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>So are you going to invest?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="102"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Berlin$<BR>That's right, technology! What did he say… It's some combination technology that he accidentally found out while he was researching. He says that it can help my hounds become healthier and it can also cure some disease or something.<BR>
I didn't really understand the difficult part but anyway, it seemed like a good cause.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n091_trader_bellin-accepting-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n091_trader_bellin-accepting-e" mid="105" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Sure.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="104"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Berlin$<BR>Erm, but I'm a little uneasy about giving him all the money before I see some results so I'm thinking of getting the materials he needs first.<BR>I hope you can help me. I will pay you well.</html>]]></talk_question>
